703899f-a.title: Brooklyn: Cropsey Avenue - 21st Avenue
703899f-a.text:
2100 Cropsey Ave., (right) at the N.W. corner of Twenty-First Ave.,
as seen across the tennis courts on the S.W. corner. On the left appear
buildings on the east side of Twenty-First Ave., at Cropsey Ave.
April 27, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
